line_1: Can stoop to pick up Strings and Sticks.
line_2: And (what's the Top of all your Tricks)

line_1: Suspend the Din of their damn'd clatt'ring Sticks.
line_2: And while their Sweet-hearts their Attention fix,

line_1: Frae less to mair it gaed to sticks;
line_2: Frae words an' aiths to clours an' nicks;

line_1: Frae less to mair it gaed to sticks;
line_2: An' monie a fallow gat his licks,

line_1: Frae less to mair it gaed to sticks;
line_2: An' some, to learn them for their tricks,
"To Rhimers in a Coach and Six.
